"""
mactrace - strace-like utility for macOS using DTrace

Traces system calls for a command and all its children, outputting JSON
suitable for timeline analysis.

Requires: sudo (DTrace needs root privileges)
Usage: sudo ./mactrace [-o output.json] command [args...]

Author: Mox (for Dan's PhD research)
"""

